# 跨域组合：表单提交

## 适用场景

用户填完表单点提交，校验输入后调用写入类云函数（新增/更新），成功后跳转或提示。

## 绑定方式

在提交按钮 View 的 `events.onClick` 挂前端 FlowSchema。流程：condition 校验必填 → callFlow 调用写入云函数 → navigate 跳转 / setData 提示。

## FlowSchema 示例（绑定在提交按钮 events.onClick）

```json
{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "check-1",
      "kind": "condition",
      "condition": {
        "left": { "kind": "dataRef", "viewId": "input-name", "key": "value" },
        "op": "!=",
        "right": { "kind": "literal", "value": "" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "submit-1",
      "kind": "callFlow",
      "functionId": "f1a2b3c4-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
      "params": {
        "name": { "kind": "dataRef", "viewId": "input-name", "key": "value" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "go-1",
      "kind": "navigate",
      "target": "list-scene",
      "mode": "redirectTo"
    },
    {
      "id": "warn-1",
      "kind": "setData",
      "viewId": "error-tip",
      "key": "text",
      "value": { "kind": "literal", "value": "名称不能为空" }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    { "id": "e1", "from": "check-1", "to": "submit-1", "branch": "true" },
    { "id": "e2", "from": "check-1", "to": "warn-1", "branch": "false" },
    { "id": "e3", "from": "submit-1", "to": "go-1" }
  ]
}
```

## 关键约定

- 前端先做轻量校验（condition），重校验/唯一性由后端云函数兜底。
- 写入失败从 submit-1 引 `branch: "error"` 边到提示节点。
- navigate.mode 取值见 primitive-flow-client-nodes（navigateTo/redirectTo/navigateBack 等）。

## 依赖

primitive-flow-common, primitive-flow-shared-nodes（condition/callFlow）, primitive-flow-client-nodes（navigate/setData）, primitive-data-cloud-function, composition-ui-form-page
